  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Use Lenz&#8217;s law to determine the direction of induced emf whenever a magnetic flux changes</item>
<item>Use Faraday&#8217;s law with Lenz&#8217;s law to determine the induced emf in a coil and in a solenoid</item>
</list></md:abstract>
  <md:language>en</md:language>
